      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-13/new-russian-defense-minister-is-devoted-to-putin-and-state-power</link>
      <description><![CDATA[俄罗斯新任国防部长安德烈·别洛乌索夫有三大爱好——艺术、国家和总统弗拉基米尔·普京。]]></description>
